:1471783,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:25:03.000Z","msg":"咪好囉<br />\n等d真遊客去到機場見到咁多封左又check又盛<br />\n覺得香港好似中國咁冇自由唔再黎<br />\n攬炒囉"},{"pid":"67cecdcb16c60afd2efec77a53317fe606b7bcff","tid":1471783,"uid":296350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7fabb3eaaa39dd2a19d11719d97ae544a3739f8a","tid":1471783,"uid":42820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b4e792b01fce845278df9994b6f34169a8c3c21e","tid":1471783,"uid":174775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:08:46.000Z","msg":"以為今次會成功，點知玩左兩日機場已經收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連續佔一星期政府必定仆直啦，點解唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"因為你唔出黎囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85B4SKb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85B4SKb.jpg&h=0fa6a6c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9U6mCy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9U6mCy.jpg&h=cfcd09f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xLjaOhA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxLjaOhA.jpg&h=95bd4188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我三日都喺度<br />\n你又去咗幾多日呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋只能夠用人數人流成事<br />\n機場絕對係要害<br />\n唔可以放棄<br />\n<br />\n第一日成功係因為成條路塞曬<br />\n佢運作唔到<br />\n如果我哋第一日嘅全部人<br />\n有車揸車<br />\n冇車搭巴士機鐵<br />\n<br />\n癱瘓去機場嘅交通<br />\n佢一樣要停<br />\n絕對和理非不損兵折將<br />\n<br />\n你咪遊車河都出埋禁制令囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95687724666004acfcc354bd2a05c9cd2662cb0","tid":1471783,"uid":158559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:25:48.000Z","msg":"咁易成功真係有啲天真<br />\n對手而家係中共呀 <br />\n不過唔好灰心 繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905a4158f9b135fc8